c: 10
v: 54
t: "Uye kana munhu wega-wega akatadza (nekusatenda muna Allah uye kunamata vamwe vanamwari) aine zvose zvepanyika uye ozoda kuzvishandisa kutenga chidzikinuro chake (hachisi kuzogamuchirwa), uye vachave mumoyo yavo nekugunun’una pavachaona mutongo, uye vachatongwa zvine ruenzaniso, uye hapana chakaipa chichaitwa kwavari"